[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Eat without stopping. Food effects apply instantly, so a snack mid-fight or mid-run doesn't break your stride.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]No pause to eat[/b] — the eating animation no longer locks the player. You keep moving (and fighting) while the food gets consumed.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Instant effects[/b] — health, mana, and any food-buff effects apply the moment you eat, instead of after the animation.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Optional: hide the food visual[/b] — toggle off the food-item visual that appears in your hand if you'd rather not see it at all.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/27]No Time For Fishing[/url] — same "skip the wait" treatment for the fishing minigame.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/37]Easy Living[/url] — a broader pile of QoL tweaks; quick-save, auto-load, menu cleanup.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/199]Auto Tools[/url] — automatic tool swapping so you don't lose time scrolling the action bar either.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30][size=3]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/size][/url]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31][size=3]Keep Alive[/size][/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Compatibility[/b][/size]

[size=3]Built and tested against the latest Steam build of Sun Haven.[/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...\steamapps\common\Sun Haven\BepInEx\plugins[/code][/size]

